33:03.281 --> 33:06.150 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hari Sreenivasan has the story
from our New
York studios.

33:06.184 --> 33:10.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The AP found
nearly 2,000
allegations of abuse and
exploitation in the

33:10.788 --> 33:12.056 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
