involved children.

33:14.959 --> 33:19.831 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And since the U.N. cannot punish
peacekeepers
from other countries, only a
fraction of the

33:19.864 --> 33:21.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
