came out against
peacekeepers.

33:58.903 --> 34:01.406 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And that's what got us started.

34:01.439 --> 34:06.711 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
From there, we just kind of --
we just counted
the number of allegations per
year that the

34:06.744 --> 34:08.513 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
U.N. had reported.

34:08.546 --> 34:12.950 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Now, you have
zoomed in
on Haiti and started to look at
almost a pattern

34:12.984 --> 34:14.752 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
