34:24.662 --> 34:27.698 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So we just went to look and see
what we could
find out in Haiti.

34:27.732 --> 34:29.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We compiled the numbers.

34:29.067 --> 34:30.802 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
