34:30.835 --> 34:33.838 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We found a lot of cases
involving children.

34:33.871 --> 34:38.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, as we were doing the
reporting -- we
have a team in Haiti and we sent
our investigative

34:38.910 --> 34:40.945 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
reporter Paisley Dodds to Haiti.

34:40.978 --> 34:46.851 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, eventually, we stumbled
across this internal
report, investigative report
from the U.N.

34:46.884 --> 34:54.859 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
