134 U.N. peacekeepers.

35:02.300 --> 35:07.371 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Now, these
children were
paid sometimes, what, a few
pennies or a dollar

35:07.405 --> 35:09.340 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
at a time for sex acts?

35:09.373 --> 35:11.175 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
TRISH WILSON: Yes.

35:11.209 --> 35:16.080 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It was low as -- there was food,
yogurt, juice
given to the children, who were
hungry, and

35:16.114 --> 35:18.049 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
