35:18.082 --> 35:23.521 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We saw -- the lowest amount we
found was 75
cents, and the highest amount
was $20.

35:23.554 --> 35:28.459 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: On the one
hand, the U.N.
conducts what you call a
thorough investigation,

35:28.493 --> 35:29.727 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
