that?

35:29.760 --> 35:31.896 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TRISH WILSON: You know, that's
what's curious.

35:31.929 --> 35:34.699 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It was really a very good
investigation by
the U.N.

35:34.732 --> 35:36.501 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
