35:52.016 --> 35:55.219 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to have sex, or lured into
having sex by these
peacekeepers.

35:55.253 --> 35:58.022 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So it was really quite a good
investigation.

35:58.055 --> 36:02.326 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
What happened after that
investigation is
what typically happens at the
U.N. and is

36:02.360 --> 36:06.097 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
one of the reasons why this is
such an important
study, or case study.

36:06.130 --> 36:11.235 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's -- the problem is that the
U.N. is in
a legal bind.

36:11.269 --> 36:16.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As you said when you opened the
segment, it
doesn't have jurisdiction over
any of these

36:16.073 --> 36:17.108 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
countries.

36:17.141 --> 36:19.277 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So the deal is, here's our
investigative report.

36:19.310 --> 36:22.380 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now it's time for Sri Lanka to
come in and
take a look at this report.

36:22.413 --> 36:27.418 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, in this case, Sri Lanka
did; 114 of those
soldiers were sent home.

36:27.451 --> 36:30.188 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But what happened after that is
anybody's
guess.

36:30.221 --> 36:31.722 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
There is no accountability.

36:31.756 --> 36:36.027 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There are no names of any of
these people,
and nobody ever went to jail.

36:36.060 --> 36:42.867 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, if you can imagine, these
kinds of corroborated
crimes against children over a
three-year

36:42.900 --> 36:47.438 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
period, corroborated by a U.N.
investigative
team, and then nothing happens.

36:47.471 --> 36:51.442 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And you point
