37:02.587 --> 37:04.088 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And it's happening in other
parts of the world.

37:04.121 --> 37:05.489 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

37:05.523 --> 37:07.024 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TRISH WILSON: Yes, there have
been allegations
