37:07.058 --> 37:09.794 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I mean, this particular story
focused on Haiti.

37:09.827 --> 37:12.730 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But we are looking at -- we are
doing a series.

37:12.763 --> 37:16.567 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is the first in a series
that looks at
what's been going on with U.N.
peacekeepers.

37:16.601 --> 37:22.506 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So there have been, sure,
problems in Central
Africa Republic, problems in
Congo with U.N.

37:22.540 --> 37:24.242 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
peacekeepers, as well as other
places.

37:24.275 --> 37:28.312 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: What's been
the reaction
from the United Nations to this?

37:28.346 --> 37:31.682 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TRISH WILSON: Well, they say
