39:36.507 --> 39:39.977 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KHALID AL-JABBOURI, Militia
Commander (through
translator): For us in this
village, Nimrud

39:40.010 --> 39:42.546 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
