39:42.580 --> 39:45.649 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This ancient city and its
antiques it's a
part of our life.

39:45.683 --> 39:50.621 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCIA BIGGS: Nimrud is the
ancient city known
as Calah in the Bible, capital
of the Assyrian

39:50.654 --> 39:55.993 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
