40:47.578 --> 40:51.949 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
My sorrow lies in the fact that
we lost something
that we were so proud of when
tourists came

40:51.982 --> 40:53.851 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to our country.

40:53.884 --> 40:59.023 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The pride we felt for them and
our civilization,
what our forefathers made for
our country,

40:59.056 --> 41:01.625 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
it's a subject that's part of
our soul.

41:01.659 --> 41:06.764 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When the Saddam regime fell in
