41:11.902 --> 41:15.406 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But ISIS, ISIS did something we
were not expecting.

41:15.439 --> 41:21.779 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCIA BIGGS: The area was taken
