explosion.

41:34.592 --> 41:40.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TOBIN HARTNELL, Archaeologist:
Every photograph,
every view I have ever seen of
Nimrud has

41:40.898 --> 41:42.099 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that temple, that ziggurat.

41:42.132 --> 41:44.635 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
