world, but
you also have to hold onto
something.

51:01.625 --> 51:05.962 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VIET THANH NGUYEN: I think I
have to be willing
to be unsettled and to be
uncomfortable.

51:05.996 --> 51:07.531 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And most people don't want that.

51:07.564 --> 51:08.665 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Most people want to be in one
place.

51:08.698 --> 51:09.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They want to feel settled and
happy.

51:09.866 --> 51:11.234 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They want to feel comfortable.

51:11.268 --> 51:13.403 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's not a good condition for
a writer,
usually.

51:13.437 --> 51:17.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, it means I have to be
willing to tolerate
that, to cultivate that, in
order to get the

51:17.707 --> 51:21.745 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
